	<article class="post-593198 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-investment-banking tag-argentina tag-china tag-economic-conditions-and-trends tag-federal-reserve-system tag-international-trade-and-world-market tag-turkey tag-united-states-economy des-economic-conditions-and-trends des-international-trade-and-world-market des-united-states-economy org-federal-reserve-system geo-argentina geo-china geo-turkey" id="post-593198">
